,"unified_progress":[0.055636,0.070438,0.078051,0.083928,0.090585,0.093038,0.094419,0.098337,0.095127,0.096052,0.081938,0.062451]},{"section":15,"text":"Plus, the specific mention of not listening to his mother might point more towards a behavior issue rather than a physical condition.","dimension":5,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.044035,0.057835,0.072028,0.078415,0.083287,0.089313,0.094005,0.10015,0.10315,0.10383,0.098351,0.075598],"unified_progress":[0.043665,0.061028,0.071889,0.079851,0.088752,0.092098,0.096321,0.1017,0.10106,0.10446,0.091056,0.068117]},{"section":16,"text":"I should also consider oppositional defiant disorder, which is a type of ADHD.","dimension":8,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034314,0.063061,0.072315,0.080412,0.086091,0.091554,0.099028,0.10188,0.10472,0.10536,0.092217,0.069052],"unified_progress":[0.033742,0.065058,0.080823,0.092977,0.095758,0.098209,0.10277,0.099761,0.09633,0.095804,0.079796,0.058972]},{"section":17,"text":"That often involves a lot of arguing and refusing to comply with adults, which might tie into not listening to his mother.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.04533,0.062286,0.072424,0.078598,0.087646,0.094502,0.099033,0.10313,0.10339,0.096387,0.085411,0.071862],"unified_progress":[0.047044,0.065956,0.078562,0.086545,0.093566,0.10112,0.099875,0.10062,0.095792,0.091813,0.077727,0.061383]},{"section":18,"text":"But the primary issue here is the restlessness and concentration problems, which are more central to ADHD.","dimension":4,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.057144,0.057339,0.065675,0.072006,0.077176,0.083251,0.088542,0.094037,0.098592,0.10041,0.10275,0.10308],"unified_progress":[0.051522,0.061828,0.070357,0.077863,0.08354,0.089051,0.090661,0.095742,0.095032,0.09713,0.09544,0.091832]},{"section":19,"text":"So putting it all together, the main symptoms point towards ADHD, specifically the combined type where he has both hyperact